Name: Dot Dash Dot
About the game: 'You were the only applicant. You have been accepted. Please report to Locke Key by Monday.' Take the role of a lighthouse operator, and use your spacebar to send Morse code messages to ships in the sea. Be quick and keep your boss satisfied, until his highly expensive cruise ship starts to sink! Can you save him and the passengers with your Morse code clicker? Features: 5 levels, Monday through Friday An endless mode after completing Friday An easy mode for the casuals Leaderboards and achievements Somewhat of a storyline
